TextEng: I want to ask you some questions.
Me want some questions from yous
Goodbye.
What do you know of the plague?
<StartCheck>[Persuade]</Start> If there is something odd here, you should tell me.
Text: <StartCheck>[설득]</Start> 여기에 이상한 일이 있다면 말씀해 주셔야 합니다.

TextEng: You know anything about the bad plague?
<StartCheck>[Persuade]</Start> If something odd here, you tell me, okay?
Text: <StartCheck>[설득]</Start> 이상한 게 있으면 말해 줘, 응?

TextEng: What do you know about attempts at a cure?
Text: 치료법을 찾으려는 시도에 대해 무엇을 아십니까?

TextEng: You know about cure attempts maybe?
I want to ask something else.
Me ask something else.
Come now, fair lass, are you keeping secrets from me?
Text: 자, 고운 아가씨, 나한테 비밀 숨기는 건가요?

TextEng: You pretty. You tell me if you hide stuff, nice lady.
Text: 예쁜 아가씨, 뭐 숨기는 거 있지?

TextEng: Something's wrong here. What is it?! Tell me or die!
Text: 여기 뭔가 잘못됐어. 뭔데?! 말하지 않으면 죽여!

TextEng: Something not right? You tell me! Tell me or die!
Text: 뭔가 이상한데? 말해! 안 말하면 죽여!

TextEng: Are you telling me everything?!
That all you have to say? Well?!
What kind of sounds?
What sounds? What there?
I'm going to go look, all right?
Me go look and you not stop me!
Text: 나 가서 볼 거야. 말리지 마!

TextEng: Me gots to check it out.
I'm going to go look. Stay out of my way.
Text: 가서 확인해 보겠습니다. 길을 비켜 주십시오.

TextEng: Do you know of anything odd? Any rumors?
You hear anything odd ever? Maybe rumor stuff?
Text: 이상한 거 들은 적 있어? 소문 같은 거?

TextEng: You seem agitated. Are you all right?
You okay? You get all shakey.
<StartCheck>[Insight]</Start> You seem agitated. Is there something hidden here?
Text: <StartCheck>[통찰]</Start> 불안해 보입니다. 이곳에 숨겨 둔 게 있습니까?

TextEng: Go over this secret again for me.
Text: 그 비밀 얘기, 한 번만 더 들려 주십시오.

TextEng: You say about secret again for me, okay?
Text: 그 비밀 다시 말해 줘, 응?

TextEng: Tell me about what is going on here! Say or die!
Text: 여기서 무슨 일이 일어나고 있는지 말해! 안 말하면 죽여!

TextEng: You say what is happening here! Do it or die!
Text: 여기서 무슨 일 났는지 말해! 안 하면 죽여!
